						<summary>

						<p>This seems to record the levy of a cess at one <hi rend="italic">nāḻi</hi> on every <hi rend="italic">kāḍi</hi> of paddy grown in the village, for the proper upkeep of the local (irrigation) tank by the same chief Viṇṇakōvaraiyaṉ Vayiri Malaiyaṉ of Viṇṇakōvaraiyar-nāḍu a sub-division of Śiṅgapura-nāḍu, with the consent of the residents of the <hi rend="italic">nāḍu.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
